README REACT BACON APP


This app explains how to use React.js with Bacon.js to connect stores, views and actions modules.
it complements Flux vision (http://facebook.github.io/flux/docs/overview.html) by utilizing a unidirectional data flow 
with Bacon.js and adding a service module to separate  externals data (API calls) to Stores.

Structure and Data Flow :

  | Services | --> |Dispatch| --> | Stores | --> |dispatch| --> |Views|
                       |                                           |
                       <--------------------------------------------


Im not a great developer. So be lenient. :)
